- You want to use this in proprietary/closed-source software
- You need maximum permissiveness and flexibility
- You are building commercial applications

**Choose GPL-3.0 if:**
- You want to ensure derivative works remain open source
- You are building free/open-source software
- You want to promote open science and collaboration

